We did it for the kids!! 👊 

Hope you raise tons of money for all the kids 
 at @bostonchildrens this year @granitetelecom, glad to be a part of it. 

Thank you Vinny and Ralphie for donating your time and hair/fur. 

And don’t worry folks, I used a brand new manscaper on Vinny 🤣 @poparotc 

#savingbyshaving #doitforthekids

node.text:
A little while ago, I got to surprise Ethan with a video call. Ethan is a young football fan, a Burkitt #lymphoma survivor, and one of the strongest kids! Thank you LLS for including me in the Light The Night #RandomActsOfLight movement and for celebrating kids like Ethan. 

Ethan, it was great to meet you, stay strong man!! To all the other kids and people fighting cancer, keep going, you got this!! 💪

Donate to help bring light to the darkness of cancer at LLS.org. #sponsored

node.text:
I am going for the championship of partying in Miami with my very own music festival during Big Game Weekend: @GronkBeach presented by @MonsterEnergy! 
Located right on the sand of Miami Beach with all my favorite artists: @DIPLO | @KASKADE | @richforever | @official_flo | @CARNAGE | @3LAU, an open bar, and amazing food! See you in Miami on Saturday, Feb 1st @GronkBeach! Tickets on sale on Thursday @11AM EST. Register now at www.GronkBeach.com

node.text:
Exciting news! I’m teaming up with @hims to tackle some of the toughest opponents men face today. Together, we’ll sideline the stigmas around hair loss and mental health to help bring out the champion in us all 🤝

Taking care of my body for performance on the field has always been a priority, but over the years, I’ve come to realize how important it is to take that same level of care off the field. Yet, finding the time and resources to make that commitment can be a challenge. Most men simply aren’t aware of the options available to them, or are uncomfortable having these tough conversations 😬

That’s where Hims comes in, a one stop shop for helping you look and feel your best, from virtual visits with healthcare providers to personalized treatments delivered to your door. This is a healthcare model that’s built to make your life easier and help you feel amazing. That’s a mission I’m excited to be a part of! Head to my link in bio to learn more.

node.text:
Congrats again to the recipients of the @buccaneers Girls in Football Scholarship! 

To Shivanie, Malia, Jordan, and Lydia:

Keep showing the world that football is a sport for everyone! You earned this. Keep up the hard work, dedication, and love for the game in college this year.

I’m glad you’ll get to kick off the season with us at @rjstadium!!
